## Adding a new route

{{ADD_ROUTE}}

<!--
  Step-by-step. Example for react-router-dom:
  1. Create the page component at src/pages/<Name>.tsx
  2. Add a <Route path=... element={<Name />} /> in src/App.tsx
  3. If auth-required, wrap in <ProtectedRoute>
  4. Add nav link in src/components/common/Sidebar.tsx if user-visible
  5. Update inventories/route-map.md (revise will catch this — but better to do it manually for new routes)
